{"tid":1453332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"禍不及妻兒","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:20:25.000Z","uid":33105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75a5c57bd1db531833a13a95e6311f9623ec92a0","tid":1453332,"uid":33105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"頭先發夢夢見有一班暴徒大叫口號衝入宿舍，拉左個狗仔出平台打，打到頭破血流之後一班附近圍觀普通市民大聲叫好，同掩護義士撤退，我都忍唔住呼應叫好，大快人心。<br />\n整個行動由開始到結束只用左5分鐘，重點係快，然後我就醒左，決定上網分享個夢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真係發夢</strong></span>，禍不及妻兒，大家千祈唔好咁做，如果未確認對方身份，好易傷及無辜"},{"pid":"96fbeb0484e515bd976f3c79c37ac5083268991c","tid":1453332,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"邊頭"},{"pid":"83d3494ece0565a972206edd134375dfd093e64a","tid":1453332,"uid":33105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"屋企附近狗宿舍已經擺設水馬，可笑<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fa2Z72H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffa2Z72H.jpg&h=e057f6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}